articles.description: Shareef O'Neal, the son of Shaquille O'Neal, is expected to commit to UCLA on Tuesday, multiple sources told ESPN. O'Neal decommitted from Arizona on Saturday, one day after ESPN reported FBI wiretaps intercepted phone conversations of coach Sean Miller.
